## Security review is recurring gate

Multiple implementation calls referenced security packet delays as the timeline blocker.

Fact: Three clients requested security evidence before pilot.
Belief: Procurement risk is often framed as technical readiness.
Value: Teams prioritize predictable launch over rapid scope expansion.
Precedent: Similar delays repeated across prior enterprise onboarding.
